      "role": "user",
      "content": "Thanks. I see what you're getting at with the \"manual intervention\" bit. It's a bit concerning though—the point of the upgrade is to move away from manual processes and rely on the AI's speed. If the new system's \"enhanced efficiency\" actually means it's going to struggle with the complex, high-touch requests our clients expect, we might run into trouble. \n\nCan you be more specific in the guide about exactly what kind of nuanced requests the new system might fail to handle? I want to make sure clients know what they're losing so they aren't blindsided when they can't get that same level of depth anymore.",
